 et de ce qui est entre eux, le Tout Clément à Qui ils ne pourront adresser aucune parole.","en":"[From] the Lord of the heavens and the earth and whatever is between them, the Most Merciful. They possess not from Him [authority for] speech.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"رَّبِّ","fr":"Seigneur","en":"Lord","tr":"rabbi","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","fr":"(de) les cieux","en":"(of) the heavens","tr":"l-samāwāti","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","fr":"et la terre","en":"and the earth","tr":"wal-arḍi","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"وَمَا","fr":"et quoi que","en":"and whatever","tr":"wamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"بَيْنَهُمَا","fr":"(est) entre les deux de eux","en":"(is) between both of them","tr":"baynahumā","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ۖ","fr":"le Tout-Miséricordieux","en":"the Most Gracious","tr":"l-raḥmāni","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"لَا","fr":"non","en":"not","tr":"lā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"يَمْلِكُونَ","fr":"ils ont puissance","en":"they have power","tr":"yamlikūna","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"مِنْهُ","fr":"de Lui","en":"from Him","tr":"min'hu","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"خِطَابًۭا","fr":"(à) adresse","en":"(to) address","tr":"khiṭāban","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":38,"verseKey":"78:38","juz":30,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ صَفًّا ۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنْ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابًا","fr":"(Ce sera) le jour où l’Esprit et les Anges se tiendront en rangées, ne disant mot, sauf ceux à qui le Tout Clément permettra (de parler) et dont la parole sera vérité.","en":"The Day that the Spirit [i.e., Gabriel] and the angels will stand in rows, they will not speak except for one whom the Most Merciful permits, and he will say what is correct.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"يَوْمَ","fr":"(Le) Jour","en":"(The) Day","tr":"yawma","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"يَقُومُ","fr":"va se tenir","en":"will stand","tr":"yaq