f":false},{"position":6,"ar":"ٱتَّخَذَ","fr":"laisser lui prendre","en":"let him take","tr":"ittakhadha","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"إِلَىٰ","fr":"vers","en":"towards","tr":"ilā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"رَبِّهِۦ","fr":"son Seigneur","en":"his Lord","tr":"rabbihi","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"مَـَٔابًا","fr":"un retourner","en":"a return","tr":"maāban","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":40,"verseKey":"78:40","juz":30,"arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنذَرْنَـٰكُمْ عَذَابًا قَرِيبًا يَوْمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلْمَرْءُ مَا قَدَّمَتْ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلْكَافِرُ يَـٰلَيْتَنِى كُنتُ تُرَٰبًۢا","fr":"Nous vous avons mis en garde contre un supplice tout proche. Ce jour-là l’homme verra ce qu’il aura fait de ses propres mains, et le mécréant dira : « Ah ! si seulement j’étais poussière ! »","en":"Indeed, We have warned you of an impending punishment on the Day when a man will observe what his hands have put forth and the disbeliever will say, \"Oh, I wish that I were dust!\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"إِنَّآ","fr":"Certes Nous","en":"Indeed We","tr":"innā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَنذَرْنَـٰكُمْ","fr":"[Nous] ont averti vous","en":"[We] have warned you","tr":"andharnākum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"عَذَابًۭا","fr":"(de) un châtiment","en":"(of) a punishment","tr":"ʿadhāban","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"قَرِيبًۭا","fr":"proche","en":"near","tr":"qarīban","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"يَوْمَ","fr":"(le) Jour","en":"(the) Day","tr":"yawma","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"يَنظُرُ","fr":"va voir","en":"will see","tr":"yanẓuru","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"ٱلْمَرْءُ","fr":"l'homme","en":"the man","tr":"l-maru","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"مَا","fr":"ce que","en":"what","tr":"mā","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"قَدَّمَتْ","fr":"ont envoyé en avant","en":"have sent forth","tr":"qaddamat","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"يَدَاهُ","fr":"son mains","en":"his hands","tr":"yadāhu","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"وَيَقُولُ","f